{"tid":50781,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"［邊個可以聽我唱歌］矛盾一生 改詞","createTime":"2016-12-22T16:52:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-05T03:03:29.000Z","uid":4353,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c8c11f50c179b85cd72054ac971ef9d8768ca3ff","tid":50781,"uid":4353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:52:53.000Z","msg":"開咗喺創意台冇人理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知呢度有冇呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 收聽請移玉步去：<br />\n<a href=\"http://soundcloud.com/user-465340638/05-sugarpova/s-eo9EA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fuser-465340638%2F05-sugarpova%2Fs-eo9EA&d=YOYowMKT4GHpmLnXTDE8RpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=e3621631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">soundcloud.com/user-465340638/05-sugarpova/s-eo9EA</a><br />\n<br />\n原歌詞由：<br />\n矛盾只因關愛座<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/29045/page/9?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/29045/page/9?ref=ios</a><br />\n裡面嘅所有巴絲所提供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一次唱，屋企冇任何PRO錄音儀器，所以電腦播音樂用電話錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n音樂用YOUTUBE人地彈嘅:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vIVcHbCR4xk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvIVcHbCR4xk&d=YOYowMKT4GHpmLnXTDE8RpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=9e4a07c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vIVcHbCR4xk</a><br />\n<br />\n暫時只係唱左半首，希望企緊地鐵火車巴士的士嘅你慢慢收聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好屌咁大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 收聽請移玉步去：<br />\n<a href=\"http://soundcloud.com/user-465340638/05-sugarpova/s-eo9EA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fuser-465340638%2F05-sugarpova%2Fs-eo9EA&d=YOYowMKT4GHpmLnXTDE8RpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=e3621631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">soundcloud.com/user-465340638/05-sugarpova/s-eo9EA</a><br />\n<br />\n歌詞：<br />\n關愛一生<br />\n<br />\n返左一天fullday過後想坐下<br />\n只想抖返一下 就坐下<br />\n心中忐忑過後還是 企出去<br />\n卻發覺經已被人 捕進鏡裏<br />\n<br />\n矛盾只因關愛座 坐得嗎<br />\n常期望有空位坐剩 然後抖下<br />\n你問我做乜唔恰下 怕被人睥嘛<br />\n坐就批鬥 廢柴 企吧<br />\n回頭看咁多關愛座 你SIT嗎<br />\n竟會沒呀嬸埋位<br />\n當佢仍然未想坐<br />\n就讓我先坐吧<br />\n這個決定多麼錯"},{"pid":"b36edeee23fcb5e9b30ef17fe5124ddc230bb5a2","tid":50781,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:53:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"003ac37957aa37d6ac15f5e4eb09ebf81374099d","tid":50781,"uid":4353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你入黎！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌屌屌屌屌屌屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc0978f54166b96186a1cef983f393a38b7ee2d","tid":50781,"uid":51291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:54:46.000Z","msg":"乜又係你呀絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19468db3a6f8a49c425759963aca649b5da30ab1","tid":50781,"uid":53911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T16:56:34.000Z","msg":"懶音"},{"pid":"24bc8e84e43c349b5af573a9d706d3922209462d","tid":50781,"uid":4353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite